      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "f-04",
      "deck_id": "flavors-discovery",
      "text": "Which flavor sounds nothing like you two?\n\nWhat exactly feels off about it?\n\nNaming by contrast counts. It's often where the real shape starts.",
