      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "f-05",
      "deck_id": "flavors-discovery",
      "text": "How much does romantic connection with others belong in your picture?\n\nPlace yourself between \"experiences only\" and \"room for feelings.\"",
